   <conbody>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The Modbus wiring for the NMC in a Reality system can be done
with a 4-wire or a 2-wire configuration. </p>
         <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">Always follow local wiring codes.</note>
         <note class="- topic/note ">It is recommended to
use 150 Ohm resistors at each end of the Modbus bus cable if the cable
is over 300 m (1000 feet) using 19200 as baud rate or over 600 m (2000
feet) using 9600 as baud rate.</note>
         <fig class="- topic/fig ">
            <title class="- topic/title ">4-Wire Configuration</title>
